        <h3>Startup Process Flow</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Application starts</strong> → Loads Comserv.pm</li>
            <li><strong>Catalyst initializes</strong> → Calls all _initialize methods</li>
            <li><strong>_initialize_ai_chat_schema()</strong> → (Currently only logs)</li>
            <li><strong>CHANGE:</strong> Call DBSchemaManager to discover Result classes</li>
            <li><strong>CHANGE:</strong> Create tables from Result definitions</li>
            <li><strong>Log output:</strong> Shows which tables created vs already exist</li>
            <li><strong>Application continues</strong> → Normal operation</li>
        </ol>

